creator: Thirty Seconds Out LLC
descriptionHtml:
Thirty Seconds Out is a lifestyle apparel brand based in the mountains of Idaho. We create designs that inspire action and performance. Like you, we value intelligent execution over excessive talk, emphasizing bettering ourselves and the world around us. We have built a strong and loyal following over the years consisting of individuals and organizations we are stoked to be associated with. Our customers are the go-getters in life. They are high achieving individuals, never satisfied with being average or accepting things as they are. They are Investment bankers, world-class climbers, firefighters, law enforcement personnel, A-list actors, Fortune 100 companies, CEOs, special operations teams, and entrepreneurs on the grind to build something awesome. You're in good company here. Welcome aboard!
With this app, your mobile shopping experience will be sweet. You will get real discounts and offers that are 100% exclusive to our mobile app shoppers. Quickly browse for that perfect t-shirt, hat, or sticker to add some fuel to your daily habits and goals. When you place an order, we will ship it quickly. Sometimes we ship your order within a few hours, depending on the time it was placed. For example, if you order a t-shirt and hat on Tuesday at 9 am MST, it will very likely ship within hours, and you'll have it in 2-5 days, depending on the shipping option you choose. Our team personally picks, packages, and ships everything. We do not drop-ship anything. We run our own warehouse that is staffed by our employees here in the little mountain town of Sun Valley, ID. If you need customer service assistance, you will get one of our team members that will personally handle things for you. We also have a warehouse in the United Kingdom and Germany, which serves all of the European Union. We opened these warehouses so that our European customers can get our products without excessive shipping, import duties, and taxes. Links to those websites are located in the menu section of this app and will direct you to those websites/stores where the shopping experience, from filling your cart to checkout, will occur not in this app but those stores, respectively. If you do live in Europe, you have the choice to be re-directed to those websites/stores, or you can shop in the app, and we will ship to you from our US warehouse. It will just cost more because of shipping and various import duties and taxes. We recommend our US customers shop using this app, while our European customers go to those websites/stores separately, but we will ship worldwide from any order placed in the app.
We appreciate the opportunity to have you as a customer, and we take that very seriously. You will find original designs here, backed by outstanding customer service and people that care about you and your experience with us. Let's get started!
